content: Can you provide an Excel table listing two services that can be used to make international calls, along with their rates per minute and any other fees associated with their usage?

Certainly! Here's an example of an Excel table listing two services that can be used for making international calls, along with their rates per minute and any associated fees:

| Service Name    | Rate per Minute | Connection Fee | Other Fees/Details                                |
|-----------------|-----------------|----------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Skype           | $0.023          | None           | Subscription plans available for lower rates     |
| Google Voice    | $0.01 - $0.20   | None           | Rates vary by country; no contracts or hidden fees|

Please note that the rates and fees are subject to change, and it is always a good idea to check the official websites of these services for the most up-to-date information.
